descript.abstract:
Census Tract boundary polygons (2010 Census) for the State of New Jersey, as of 2012.
For additional documentation, see the US Census Bureau, TIGER data Web site.
descript.purpose: Data reprojected by NJOIT OGIS for use in state Web maps and for redistribution to GIS desktop users.
descript.supplinf:
Shapefile in geographic coordinates was downloaded from the US Census Bureau Web site for New Jersey Partnership Shapefile Batch Download on January 7, 2013:
http://www.census.gov/geo/partnerships/pvs/bas/st34_nj.html
The data were developed in partnership with the NJ State Redistricting Commission, following the 2010 U.S. Census.
The shapefile was then reprojected to NAD83 NJ State Plane coordinates, US Survey feet, and several empty attributes were deleted.

Data in geographic coordinates can be obtained directly from the Census Bureau Web site.

procstep.procdesc: U.S. Census Bureau TIGER shapefile, 2012 release of 2010 Census Tracts, was reprojected to NAD83 NJ State Plane feet. Metadata record was created reflecting OGIS processing and redistribution of the projected data by the State of New Jersey. Some information was incorporated from Census Bureau documentation.

Table compare and symmetrical difference tools were run to compare this shapefile to the census tract polygon shapefile released for the 2010 census. The only changes noted were minor spatial changes along the exterior boundaries of New Jersey.
